Lead_progress_chart__1.label: Lead progress chart (Age)
Lead_progress_chart__1.query: q = load "${App.Datasets.FscDemoLead.FullyQualifiedName}";q = group q by all; this_lead = foreach q generate "1 - This Lead/Referral Age" as 'Display', {{cell(Selected_lead_1.result, 0, "sum_LeadAge").asObject()}} as 'Value', "{{cell(Selected_lead_1.result, 0, "Age Status").asObject()}}" as 'Age Status';avg_for_source = foreach q generate "2 - Avg for source: " + "{{cell(Selected_lead_1.result, 0, "LEADSOURCE").asObject()}}" as 'Display', {{cell(Conversion_rate_for__1.result, 0, "Avg Days to Convert").asObject()}} as 'Value', " " as 'Age Status';avg_for_product = foreach q generate "3 - Avg for Type: " + "{{cell(Selected_lead_1.result, 0, "PRODUCTINTEREST").asObject()}}" as 'Display', {{cell(Conversion_rate_for__2.result, 0, "Avg Days to Convert").asObject()}} as 'Value', " " as 'Age Status';overall_avg = foreach q generate "4 - Overall Avg" as 'Display', {{cell(Average_time_to_conv_1.result, 0, "Avg days to convert").asObject()}} as 'Value', " " as 'Age Status';result = union this_lead, avg_for_source, avg_for_product, overall_avg;result = group result by ('Display','Age Status');result = foreach result generate 'Display', 'Age Status', sum('Value') as 'Value';

Lead_progress_chart__2.label: Lead progress chart (Activities)
Lead_progress_chart__2.query: q = load "${App.Datasets.FscDemoLead.FullyQualifiedName}";q = group q by all; this_lead = foreach q generate "1 - This Lead/Referral" as 'Display', {{cell(Selected_lead_1.result, 0, "ACTIVITYTOUCHES").asObject()}} as 'Value', "{{cell(Selected_lead_1.result, 0, "Activity Status").asObject()}}" as 'Acitivty Status';avg_for_source = foreach q generate "2 - Avg for source: " + "{{cell(Selected_lead_1.result, 0, "LEADSOURCE").asObject()}}" as 'Display', {{cell(Conversion_rate_for__1.result, 0, "E").asObject()}} as 'Value', " " as 'Acitivty Status';avg_for_product = foreach q generate "3 - Avg for Type: " + "{{cell(Selected_lead_1.result, 0, "PRODUCTINTEREST").asObject()}}" as 'Display', {{cell(Conversion_rate_for__2.result, 0, "E").asObject()}} as 'Value', " " as 'Acitivty Status';overall_avg = foreach q generate "4 - Overall Avg" as 'Display', {{cell(Lead_metrics_1.result, 0, "Avg Activities for Conv Lead").asObject()}} as 'Value', " " as 'Acitivty Status';result = union this_lead, avg_for_source, avg_for_product, overall_avg;result = group result by ('Display','Acitivty Status');result = foreach result generate 'Display', 'Acitivty Status', sum('Value') as 'Value';
